          <a href="/blog/factors-that-impact-your-interview-scores">Factors that impact your interview scores</a>
        </h1>
        <div class="meta article-meta">
          <span class="date"><time class="published dt-published" datetime="2016-04-07" itemprop="datePublished">April 7, 2016</time></span>
          <span class="author">Fernando Delgado</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="special-content">
        <figure class="sqs-block-image-figure intrinsic">
